    aiu:partOfInventory aiu:inv2024 ;
    aiu:useCaseName "SERVIR Ecosystem and Carbon Management: Automation of land cover and change mapping, including forest disturbance due to roads and mining. SERVIR is applying machine learning and deep learning techniques on satellite data to automate the classification and identification of land surface activities at the scale of 10s of meters."^^xsd:string .

