    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_1_4,  # Strategic planning and scaling under uncertainty
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: R is a product that incorporates fundamental modeling, AI and machine learning techniques for predictive modeling, natural language processing, computer vision and deep learning. This product assists in the design and development of  sophisticated economic models to analyze markets. This is a general-purpose tool for quantitative analysis and modeling that is generally used for analyzing and modeling market conditions and scenarios. While it is not practical to inventory all the ways in which this tool is used in individual cases, when the tool is used to develop evidence offered in litigation, ordinary rules of evidence apply.

Expected benefits: Provides ATR with the ability to analyze, summarize, synthesize, and manage various data sources and data formats to support economic and statistical analysis of corporation and market conditions. ATR relies heavily on data analytical tools to support mico - and macro-level analysis. Predictive model outputs, statistical analysis, natural language processing, text analytics, forecasting predictions, optimization recommendations, risk analysis scores, anomaly detection, 
customer segmentation groupings, decision tree analysis paths"""^^xsd:string .

