    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Databricks is a product that incorporates fundamental modeling, AI and machine learning techniques for predictive modeling, natural language processing, computer vision and deep learning. This product assists in the design and development of sophisticated economic models to analyze markets. This is a general-purpose tool for quantitative analysis and modeling that is generally used for analyzing and modeling market conditions and scenarios. While it is not practical to inventory all the ways in which this tool is used in individual cases, when the tool is used to develop evidence offered in litigation, ordinary rules of evidence apply.

