aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1835 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: DEA is a data-driven organization that integrates data and analytics capabilities across its mission. The purpose of this use case is to search, monitor, and analyze wide variety of public-facing unstructured and structured data sources such as scientific literature, social media, dark web, news, public records, public internet forums, and more to protect American communities and save lives. 

Expected benefits: This use case enables DEA to gain key insights at exponentially higher speeds with lower costs by fusing variety of data sources. Benefits include: operational insights, emerging threat detection, agent safety, public safety, improved mission-enabling services, etc. Outputs vary by use case."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1836 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_3_2,  # Quality, reliability, and consistency
        aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: DEA is a data-driven organization that integrates data and analytics capabilities across its mission. In the course of analyzing drug seizures, chemists within the Forensic Sciences Division encounter uncommon and or initially unknown chemical compounds. The purpose of this use case is to identify unknown drug samples by comparing them against a library of known spectra.

Expected benefits: For less commonly encountered compounds, this use case saves time and provides information for human decision-making. The  comparison/matching also fulfills requirements to provide spectra from known/traceable materials. Outputs a recommended list of best matches to be decided upon by the analyst and included in the case file as supporting evidence for the identified substances reported."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1837 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: DEA is a data-driven organization that integrates data and analytics capabilities across its mission. The purpose of this use case is to utilize a sensor system to detect gunshots for physical security. This system is not for operational matters. 

Expected benefits: To assist DEA with protecting DEA employees in the event of an active shooter. Sensors report gunshot activity."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1838 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_7_4,  # Ethics, fraud, and whistleblowing
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: DEA is a data-driven organization that integrates data and analytics capabilities across its mission. The purpose of this use case is to enhance the investigative process and search for patterns and relationships in financial transactions including cryptocurrencies to support drug trafficking and money laundering investigations.

Expected benefits: Enhances the detection and prevention of financial crimes related to ongoing investigations. Outputs include recommended results and data visualizations."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1839 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_7_4,  # Ethics, fraud, and whistleblowing
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: DEA is a data-driven organization that integrates data and analytics capabilities across its mission. The purpose of this use case is to enhance the investigative process and search for patterns and relationships in financial transactions including cryptocurrencies to support drug trafficking and money laundering investigations.

Expected benefits: Enhances the detection and prevention of financial crimes related to ongoing investigations. Outputs include recommended results and data visualizations."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1840 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_7_4,  # Ethics, fraud, and whistleblowing
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: DEA is a data-driven organization that integrates data and analytics capabilities across its mission. The purpose of this use case is to enhance the investigative process and search for patterns and relationships in financial transactions including cryptocurrencies to support drug trafficking and money laundering investigations.

Expected benefits: Enhances the detection and prevention of financial crimes related to ongoing investigations. Outputs include recommended results and data visualizations."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1841 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: DEA is a data-driven organization that integrates data and analytics capabilities across its mission. The purpose of this use case is to automate the validation and summarization of ARCOS data for further analysis.

Expected benefits: To save time and effort of fully manual review of ARCOS data. Outputs a list of recommendations with validated data with summary information."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1842 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: DEA is a data-driven organization that integrates data and analytics capabilities across its mission. The purpose of this use case is to rank CSA transaction data based on the factors identified/calculated as part of a manual analysis.

Expected benefits: To reduce time and effort of manually ranking. Outputs a data visualization that highlights activity, based on certain factors, and includes a ranking."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1843 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: DEA has a mission to protect communities and save lives. It requires a need to understand communications within criminal operations. Multi-language machine transcription of audio files is intended to filter massive audio files to relevant data for review. This is one feature of a larger system.

Expected benefits: To allow search of audio files to identify which parts of the conversations should be reviewed and interpreted officially by human translators and analysts for discovery purposes. Outputs vary by use case."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1844 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_2_4,  # Customer experience, satisfaction, and retention
        aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: DEA is a data-driven organization that integrates data and analytics capabilities across its mission. The purpose of this use case is to improve the effectiveness of the Diversion Control Registrant Call Center by automating the routing of incoming calls, providing answers to common questions for Diversion Control Registrant call center agents to identify and quickly propose steps toward resolution, and monitoring customer feedback.

Expected benefits: To expedite responding to registrant needs with timeliness and consistency of DEA's customer service posture to DEA registrants. To decrease labor costs while maintaining high levels of customer service to DEA registrants. To capture needed improvements to service for implementation. Outputs a recommended course of action with recommended response for the call center operator to the DEA registrant to resolve the interaction, a priority classification and response to customers needing higher level intervention of call center staff, and a report that summarizes the survey responses with quantifiable and qualitative metrics."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1845 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_3_3,  # Innovation pace and responsiveness
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: The purpose of this use case is to create a R&D environment to enable DEA to test and prototype Generative AI based solutions.

Expected benefits: To provide a safe environment to prototype and test experimental AI based use cases. Outputs vary based on the use cases."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1846 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: DEA has a mission to protect communities and save lives. The purpose of this use case is to generate images for use in training materials.

Expected benefits: To reduce the amount of time and resources needed to develop training aids and graphical inserts for online Computer Based Training (CBT). Outputs graphical content based on the queries entered by users."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1847 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: DEA has a mission to protect communities and save lives. Drone technology uses AI for autonomous navigation and obstacle avoidance. The purpose of this use case is to enable more proficient drone operation and to support agent safety.
 
Expected benefits: This use case supports human drone operators and pilots in deploying drones. It reduces resources and allows trained drone operators to focus on real-time operational needs. Outputs reports and analytics on drones operations."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1848 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: DEA has a mission to protect communities and save lives. Prediction of Nuclear Magnetic Resonance (NMR) spectra based upon chemical structures in an important component of structural elucidation when identifying known and unknown chemicals.

Expected benefits: Fast processing and interpretation of nuclear magnetic resonance spectra. Outputs predicted labels for the spectra."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1849 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_3_2,  # Quality, reliability, and consistency
        aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: DEA operates a large number of systems, services, and applications within its IT environments. The reliable performance of these systems is critical for to DEA to carry out its mission. The purpose of this use case is to automate observability processes (metrics, logs, traces, etc.), enhance operational efficiency, and improve performance and reliability of services and applications within DEA IT environments.  

Expected benefits: To facilitate expedited information retrieval, discoveries within unstructured data to support timely mission-enabling functions. Outputs the recommended results of root cause, impact analysis, automated remediation recommendations, and predictive insights."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1850 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_8_1,  # Technology and data alignment
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: DEA is a data-driven organization that integrates data and analytics capabilities across its mission. The purpose of this use case was to validate and propose standardization updates for Automation of Reports and Consolidated Orders System (ARCOS) data to improve accuracy and conciseness.

Expected benefits: To improve the data capture and processing within Automation of Reports and Consolidated Orders System (ARCOS). No AI outputs were generated. The contract period of performance has ended."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1851 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3,  # Automation and AI enablement
        aiu:BG_9_2 ;  # Regulatory and policy adaptability
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: DEA is a data-driven organization that integrates data and analytics capabilities across its mission. The purpose of this use case is to utilize Generative AI to classify, summarize, organize and analyze public comments on Regulations.gov.

Expected benefits: To save time in manually reviewing large quantity of comments with AI-enabled categorization, summarization, and trends analysis to support appropriate prioritization for DEA's review and validation. Outputs categorizes, summarizes, filters, flags, and organizes per queries inputted by DEA."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1852 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_8_1,  # Technology and data alignment
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: DEA will migrate to a FedRAMP authorized environment, and will have access to AI/ML tools which may enable more data driven decision making.

Expected benefits: To support expedited data collaboration and analytics. Outputs vary by use case."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1853 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_7_1,  # Regulatory and legal compliance
        aiu:BG_8_1,  # Technology and data alignment
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: The DEA is responsible for coordination and cooperation with federal, state and local law enforcement officials on mutual drug enforcement efforts and enhancement of such efforts through potential interstate and international investigations beyond local or limited federal jurisdictions and resources. The purpose of this use case is to enable local law enforcement to identify individuals with whom they come into contact as appropriate. DEA does not manage this system.

Expected benefits: To quickly and accurately identify individuals with whom law enforcement officials come into contact as appropriate. The AI system pulls data from multiple sources in order to find identifying information. These include data collected from: 1) Local law enforcement, i.e., the names, addresses, license plate numbers, and phone numbers of people with whom they've been in contact), 2) Jail bookings and inmates, 3) DMV, 4) License Plate Readers (LPRs) used by local law enforcement, and 4) ARJIS and SDLAW."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1854 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Provides AI-assisted research to help streamline legal research and document review. 

Expected benefits: Increases the speed at which attorneys can review and evaluate caselaw to determine if it is applicable to their current investigations. Case law recommendations"""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1855 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_3_2,  # Quality, reliability, and consistency
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Aids attorneys with grammar and sentence structure to enable stronger written product.

Expected benefits: Provide stronger written products. Briefs, summaries, and any other written work product."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1856 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_8_2,  # Cybersecurity and protection
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Certain tools are used department-wide to provide endpoint detection; threat intelligence, analysis, and response; and related services. These tools include, for example, CrowdStrike, Zscaler, Splunk, Lookout, Palo Alto Networks, and Cisco Secure Network Analytics.

Expected benefits: To help the Department more quickly identify and respond to threats and indicators of compromise from systems. Recommendations related to potential IT security threats"""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1857 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_7_1,  # Regulatory and legal compliance
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Department of Justice components use electronic litigation (eLitigation) tools for a broad range of purposes, including support of investigations, litigation, and FOIA and Privacy Act processes. Most of these tools are commercial-off-the-self products that are commonly used outside of government, such as Everlaw and Relativity. These tools increasingly integrate AI capabilities that can assist with tasks core to the mission of the Department, such as surfacing potentially discoverable information in voluminous collections of emails, text messages, or other electronic records; locating potentially inculpatory or exculpatory evidence in voluminous electronic data; and identifying material that may be appropriate for disclosure or withholding according to applicable legal rules and privileges.

Expected benefits: eLitigation tools can offer substantial benefits over exclusively human review of voluminous electronic information: they can be faster, more accurate and consistent, and more efficient. 

Please note: These tools are used in contexts that are rights-impacting, but the nature and details of AI uses vary, which may affect whether particular uses are rights-impacting. Outputs vary by use case."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1858 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Forensic analysis tools used to extract, analyze, search, and organize digital evidence and datasets.

Expected benefits: Increases the efficiency of extracting data from devices and of analyzing/searching for pertinent data within devices and datasets. Outputs vary by use case."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1859 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: DOJ employees use services such as Google and Bing to retrieve information on a variety of subjects.

Expected benefits: Streamline the information-gathering processes. Recommended search results"""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1860 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Conduct legal research.

Expected benefits:  Improving accuracy and efficiency of legal research. Recommends caselaw and other legal materials (such as statutes, regulations, and scholarly articles) and, in some circumstances, an overview of the law in response to queries."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1861 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_6_1,  # Talent, skills, and workforce strategy
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Interactive tool using generative AI to customize learning environments for the workforce.

Expected benefits: Training tailored to individual needs. Training recommendations."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1862 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: To automate engagement with IT helpdesk personnel for IT requests. ServiceNow is a cloud-based platform that digitizes and automates workflows and  helps organizations work more efficiently and effectively. ServiceNow automates incident triage and classification and can handle routine inquires and simple tasks to free up resources to focus on higher priority issues. 

Expected benefits: Allows IT support to common and simple requests 24/7.  ServiceNow provides a scalable solution that supports faster and more responsive service delivery and cost savings across the organization. Virtual agents handle common inquires that free staff for higher priority issues while predictive intelligence offers data-driven insights to improve decision-making and optimizing resource allocation. Consistent processing helps reduce errors and enhances user experience. Automated service requests
Incident resolution recommendations
Virtual agency responses
Data insights and analytics reports
Search results and recommendations 
Documented and categorized knowledge-based articles."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1863 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_7_1,  # Regulatory and legal compliance
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Performing legal research.

Expected benefits:  Improving accuracy and efficiency of legal research. Recommends caselaw and other legal materials (such as statutes, regulations, and scholarly articles) and, in some circumstances, an overview of the law in response to queries."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1864 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_7_1,  # Regulatory and legal compliance
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Performing legal research.

Expected benefits:  Improving accuracy and efficiency of legal research. Recommends caselaw and other legal materials (statutes, regulations, scholarly articles, etc.) and, in some circumstances, an overview of the law in response to queries."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1865 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: ENRD uses ArcGIS to create, view, and edit GIS maps.  Although ENRD's ArcGIS license includes a feature known as GeoAI, ENRD has not yet used it, and there are currently no work flows involving the use of GeoAI. ENRD might use GeoAI in an appropriate case to screen a set of aerial photographs and identify objects or features in the photos. Pre-trained models offered by ArcGIS include models purportedly capable of identifying oil well pads and oil tanks, performing OCR on maps, and classifying land cover from certain image sources. The software also reportedly allows the training of custom models, although ENRD currently has no plans to create any. ENRD might use GeoAI to assist in mapping addresses contained in the text of a set of documents or to analyze large sets of tabular data, such as the geographical distribution of phone records.

Expected benefits: Faster evaluation of aerial photographs and documents that contain location information and discovery of patterns and clusters not readily apparent in data. Data points on GIS maps indicating the presence of objects, features, or other locations of interest; choropleth maps depicting analytical results; statistical summary graphs and tables; repeatable analytic models."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1866 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Parallel Search helps attorneys and paralegals identify cases that are relevant to particular points of law by allowing them to describe the case they are looking for in plain language. 

Expected benefits: Faster legal research Legal citations to cases."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1867 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_6_2,  # Engagement, culture, and incentives
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Qualtrics is a cloud-based service that can send out survey and record responses. ENRD uses it to send out questionnaires to its own employees to gather feedback on issues such as training needs and student feedback on training sessions. ENRD also uses Qualtrics to collect victim impact statements and to collect public input in environmental justice matters. 

Qualtrics includes a sentiment analysis feature, but ENRD has not used it. Sentiment analysis can review narrative responses from respondents and summarize the overall sentiment of a group of respondents and surface insights and issues from a large number of responses. Future uses of this tool are uncertain.

Expected benefits:  Qualtrics can provide immediate analysis of respondent sentiment and surface insights. It can reduce the number of hours and effort spent reading and scoring narrative responses and summarizing the overall opinion on the subject. Survey responses and reports summarizing data from responses."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1868 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: SimplyFile uses AI to learn a users email filing habits and then predict where the user will want to move each email by displaying a list of suggested filing locations. This allows users to file their emails with a single button click, rather than having to click and drag them to the correct folders.

Expected benefits: Faster and more accurate email filing A sorted list of predicted filing locations (Outlook folders)"""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1869 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Veritone is available to ENRD through JMD. ENRD has not used Veritone, but might use it to help with discovery or investigation if the need emerges in an appropriate case or matter. Veritone can transcribe media files collected from an agency in response to a discovery request; provide machine translation (e.g., of foreign-language documents produced by an opposing party in litigation); assist with redactions of audio, video, or images obtained from agencies for civil discovery; and identify and track objects in video. ENRD might use such tools to perform a preliminary screening on large volumes of materials obtained in an investigation or in discovery. All materials, whether flagged during screening or not, would then be provided to counsel for further action in compliance with legal requirements.

Expected benefits:  Faster screening of large volumes of electronic materials or information that may be of interest in an investigation or discovery. Transcribed or translated text, tagged media files, and draft redactions for media files."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1870 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_4,  # Alignment with stakeholder expectations and social impact
        aiu:BG_6_2,  # Engagement, culture, and incentives
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Zoom provides automatic closed captioning at live training events, depositions, and court hearings. Closed captioning is provided for the benefit of the hearing impaired. Transcripts may be temporarily saved, e.g., for the convenience of the presenter to note areas in which the training could be improved next time, but otherwise the transcripts serve no official purpose and do not replace court reporters for generating official transcripts of depositions and hearings.

Expected benefits: Increased accessibility. Provide closed captioning text at live events. Closed captions"""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1871 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_3,  # Crisis readiness and communications
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Media monitoring service that allows users to search, analyze, and create reports using specific criteria. Facilitates searches in broadcasts, online news, social media, and podcasts. 

Expected benefits: Awareness of media mentions. Curated reports about public media presence."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1872 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: The Draft One product can be used by investigators to produce draft report narratives.  Investigators can use Auto-Transcribes to turn speech from audio sources into text. Investigators can leverage Redaction Assistant to detect and redact common objects found in body-worn videos.  Investigators can also use Audio Redaction to redacting the corresponding audio and transcript.

Expected benefits: Cost savings, reducing time to prepare, and increased efficiencies during litigation. Review Assistant to Draft reports narratives, text audio conversion, and edited video."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1873 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Curating publicly available information to assist with litigation. 

Expected benefits: Provides the capability to quickly aggregate and distill publicly available data to assist with litigation. Reports to assist with litigation (recommendation)"""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1874 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_8_2,  # Cybersecurity and protection
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: User Behavior Analytics detect anomalies. This tool uses machine learning to identify security threats.

Expected benefits: It allows large complex datasets to be analyzed effectively. It outputs reports and alerts for anomalies."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1875 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Security enhancement to Field Offices.

Expected benefits: enhanced security -"""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1876 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_1,  # Technology and data alignment
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Tool facilitates more efficient categorization and analysis of publicly available information.

Expected benefits: more efficient categorization and analysis -"""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1877 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_7_1,  # Regulatory and legal compliance
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Tool to conduct authorized searches of photos of individuals pertinent to an ongoing investigation against publicly available images to generate investigative leads.

Expected benefits: generation of investigative leads -"""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1878 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: System which uses optical character recognition and language translation to process information from physical or digital documents. This tool is not used for identification/authentication.

Expected benefits: process information from documents Capability returns a list of detected words as well as a confidence score in additional English text for a specified word or phrase
It returns the coordinates of a detected biometric, as well a confidence score and the type of biometric detected.
It is used to automatically detect biometric data on tenprint cards and other documents in order to include the data in biometric submissions for the other systems."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1879 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Program uses character recognition to read and identify license plates. 

Expected Benefits: License plate reader technology assists in locating vehicles associated with persons of interest. License plate values"""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1880 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Quicker processing of calls coming into threat intake examiners when the caller information can be gathered and put into data fields automatically.

Expected benefits: Reduced customer wait time. text"""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1881 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
