Expected benefits: generation of investigative leads -"""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1882 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Multi-language text extraction and translation tools.

Expected benefits: Transcribing of audio and video files into text which enables users to search for pertinent information. -"""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1883 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_6_1,  # Talent, skills, and workforce strategy
        aiu:BG_6_3,  # Retention, burnout, and leadership pipelines
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Two models work in tandem:  Attrition Model: The basic goal of the model is to provide probabilities of attrition for all employees over different time windows, so that the total future attrition for arbitrary subsets of employees can be estimated. Background Model: The Background Model has two ML sub models related to successful background/on-boarding process clearances: chances of successful completion, and timeline for successful completions. Individual-level results are not provided to personnel involved in recruiting or retaining those individuals.

Expected Benefits: When the models are used successfully, the FBI's staffing fill rates will increase ensuring the organization has the necessary manpower to complete its objectives. The models produce .csv files which are then incorporated into various database tables and reports for end users to consume. Outputs are general estimates and are not attributable to specific individuals."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOJ_1884 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_7_1,  # Regulatory and legal compliance
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Purpose: Tool facilitates audio and video recording within FBI custodial interview rooms, consistent with DOJ and FBI policy.

Expected benefits: Prevents loss of required audio and video data within FBI custodial interview rooms Audio and video recordings"""^^xsd:string .

