        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "To automatically translate unofficial documents into various languages quickly and easily, without the time and expense needed for human translation. Language translation of published documents and websites using natural language processing models."^^xsd:string .

