    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Automatic analysis of recorded calls made to Benefits Advisors in the DOL Interactive Voice Response (IVR) center. AI is not used for analysis, AI is used only for transcription The output is a transcription of calls. The AI is only doing the transcriptions"^^xsd:string .

