    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_2_4,  # Customer experience, satisfaction, and retention
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Keep up with friends on the fly with Stories and Notes that disappear after 24 hours.
Start group chats and share unfiltered moments with your Close Friends.
Share memories from recent events or trips in Feed.
Turn your life into a movie and discover short, entertaining videos on Instagram with Reels.
Customize your posts with exclusive templates, music, stickers and filters. NLP, Communications"""^^xsd:string .

