aiu:plan_2024_DOL_567 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_4,  # Alignment with stakeholder expectations and social impact
        aiu:BG_6_1,  # Talent, skills, and workforce strategy
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Kurzweil 1000 makes printed or electronic text accessible to people with blindness and visual impairments, speaking text aloud in a variety of natural-sounding voices that can be modified to individual preferences. NLP: text to voice. Audio output from text input"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOL_568 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Microsoft Office Suite is a collection of productivity software applications developed by Microsoft. It is widely used for various personal, educational, and business tasks create slideshows combining text, images, and multimedia. creating, editing, and formatting text documents"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2051 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_7_1,  # Regulatory and legal compliance
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "This Compliance Plan conveys DOTs approach to achieving consistency with OMB Memorandum M-24-10 Advancing Governance, Innovation, and Risk Management for Agency Use of Artificial Intelligence. The plan aligns with M-24-10s three main pillars of Strength Provides the Department with a roadmap for accelerating the responsible use of AI and complying with OMB directives."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2052 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_3_3,  # Innovation pace and responsiveness
        aiu:BG_8_1,  # Technology and data alignment
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "The ART Network is the shared service environment for AI research and development activities that provides researchers with access to a rapid AI innovation, exploration, development, and sharing platform using secure and approved IT infrastructure. The ART Network shared service accelerates AI-enabled research at the Department by providing researchers with direct access to an established platform that contains all available AI tools for that environment rather than making changes to an existing env"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2053 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_3_3,  # Innovation pace and responsiveness
        aiu:BG_8_1,  # Technology and data alignment
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Provides operational AI use case developers with access to shared environments with all OCIO-cleared AI functionality for use case experimentation, development, and initial data and model risk management identification and mitigation. The OPSLAB shared service accelerates AI-enabled operational use case development at the Department by providing AI developers  with direct access to an established platform that contains all available AI tools for that environment rather than making chan"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2054 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_8_1,  # Technology and data alignment
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "The TrAIN is the set of shared service environments for operational AI use cases that provides AI developers with a pre-established, secure AI-enabled environments for development, testing and deployment under the Chief AI Officer's compliance and risk ma The TrAIN shared service accelerates AI-enabled operational use case deployment at the Department by providing AI developers  with direct access to an established platform that contains all available AI tools for that environment rather than making change"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2055 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_1_1,  # Direction, ambition, and coherence
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "The AISCC provides all DOT employees and contractors with a website for getting educated on AI topics, get inspired by DOT and external use cases and capabilities, collaborate with internal and external AI communities of practice, partner with AI subject Provides the Department's north star for the delivery of AI education, inspiration, and direction to the workforce."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2056 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Secure enterprise AI-enabled document generative AI capabilities. Research and operating administrations are able to use application program interfaces (APIs) to develop employee productivity enhancing solutions for querying user-provided documents."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2057 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_8_1,  # Technology and data alignment
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Secure enterprise AI-enabled question and answer ChatBot capabilities for natural language querying of documents and data. Provides the Department with secure enterprise-wide LLM ChatBot capabilities that can be tailored to specific use cases."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2058 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_1_4,  # Strategic planning and scaling under uncertainty
        aiu:BG_6_1,  # Talent, skills, and workforce strategy
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "CPC Outlook Generator (COG) is a front end Graphical User Interface built to interact with a data model called CPC Onboarding Success Evaluator (COSE), a machine learning model capable of predicting how many Certified Professional Controller (CPCs) the FA Based on what-if scenario, the system provides a graphical representation of a 5 or 10 year CPC staffing outlook (which is the predictive component provided by the ML).  Alongside with the cost (training and salary) the \"when\" the target shifts (is it ear"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2059 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_3_2,  # Quality, reliability, and consistency
        aiu:BG_4_3,  # Internal controls, procedures, and performance management
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "AI-based voice recognition of Air Traffic Control (ATC) and pilot communications associated with a flight is required for enhanced and accurate delay reporting and attribution.  Many delay events, such as vectoring, are not currently reported/detected/acc The output of the AI system is data that captures a delay and the associated cause.  This will be combined with other data sources to provide a more accurate representation of a flight."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2060 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_3_2,  # Quality, reliability, and consistency
        aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "\"Utilize equipment telemetry data, statistical modeling and Machine Learning to predict equipment failures before they occur.  This will improve operational efficiency and safety by reducing unscheduled outages and/or shortening outage times as replacemen Utilize equipment telemetry data, statistical modeling and Machine Learning to predict equipment failures before they occur.  This will improve operational efficiency and safety by reducing unscheduled outages and/or shortening outage times as replacement"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2061 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "The use of AI modeling can categorize the types of events based on the information provided in the accident and incident report and its result will support the safety metric calculation. The AI system can classify the event types such as mid-air collisions, flight into terrain accidents, and turbulence events for a given accident or incident reports."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2062 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Automated review of accident narratives.. Classification of aircraft accidents as a
 - runway collision
 - taxiway collision
 - runway excursion
 - not a surface event"""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2063 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "To classify surface Mandatory Occurrence Reports (MORs) to reduce the amount of manual event review. Classes  - runway excursion, runway incursion, surface incident."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2064 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_3_2,  # Quality, reliability, and consistency
        aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "To transcribe recorded radio communications between pilots and air traffic controllers operating within the national airspace. Text transcriptions and speaker role (pilot/controller)"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2065 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Unmanned Aircraft Systems (UAS) are a source of potential safety risk.  Manual data exploration by a human is labor and time consuming.  Automatic data mining can help to identify safety issues. Binary classification (yes/no) label for UAS event detection"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2066 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "to label radio communication transcripts according to the HP Taxonomy labeling system. One of 400 HP taxonomy labels."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2067 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_7_1,  # Regulatory and legal compliance
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "The AVS International office is required to identify means of compliance to ICAO Standards and Recommended Practices (SARPs).  Both SARPs and means of compliance evidence are text paragraphs scattered across thousands of pages of documents.  AOV identifie"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2068 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "AVS identified a need to derive the joint aircraft system codes (JASC) chapter codes from the narrative description within service difficulty reports (SDR), a form of safety event reporting from aircraft operators. A team of graduate students at George Ma"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2069 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """The AI/ML tool helps detect and predict where precipitation currently is and where it will be at the future at various altitudes in parts of the NAS that do not have traditional ground based weather radar. 
Benefits are better weather dectection and avoid The output of the system is meant to simulate weather radar where cooler colors (blues and greens) correspond to light precip where hotter colors (yellow, oranges and red) indicate heavy precip and/or more intense precipitation. A similar process is down"""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2070 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_7_1,  # Regulatory and legal compliance
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "The Multiple Airport Route Separation (MARS) program is developing a safety case for reduced separation standards between Performance Based Navigation (PBN) routes in terminal airspace. These new standards may enable deconfliction of airports in high-dema"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2071 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Before digitization: 
* The Certification Services Oversight Process (CSOP) is a manually intensive paper process 

* Requires the public and small businesses to provide input for Certification requests

* No external applicant tracking which results in p "Before digitization: 

* The Certification Services Oversight Process (CSOP) is a manually intensive paper process 

* Requires the public and small businesses to provide input for Certification requests

* No external applicant tracking which results in"""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2072 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_3_2,  # Quality, reliability, and consistency
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Successfully demonstrated use of an AI capability to analyze camera images of a wind sock to produce highly accurate surface wind speed and direction information in remote areas that dont have a weather observing sensor."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2073 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_3_2,  # Quality, reliability, and consistency
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "ROMIO is an operational demonstration to evaluate the feasibility to uplink convective weather information to aircraft operating over the ocean and remote regions. Capability converted weather satellite data, lightning and weather prediction model data in"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2074 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_3_3,  # Innovation pace and responsiveness
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Description: Utilize deep learning models for predicting head kinematics directly from crash videos. The utilization of deep learning techniques enables the extraction of 3D kinematics from 2D views, offering a viable alternative for calculating head kine Angular velocity - injury prediction"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2075 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Description: Utilize deep learning for predicting crash parameters, Delta-V (change in velocity) and PDOF (principal direction of force), directly from real-world crash images. Delta-V and PDOF are two most important parameters affecting injury outcome. D Delta-V & PDOF"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2076 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_3_2,  # Quality, reliability, and consistency
        aiu:BG_3_3,  # Innovation pace and responsiveness
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Description: Deep learning computer vision algorithms aimed at analyzing aggregate particle size grading.
Input: Images of ballast cross sections Ballast fouling index"""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2077 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Description: DeepCNet-based neural network to identify and classify track-related  features (e.g., track components, such as fasteners and ties) for \"\"change detection\"\" applications. Input: Line-scan images from rail-bound inspection systems. Notification of changes from status quo or between different inspections based on geolocation."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2078 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_3_2,  # Quality, reliability, and consistency
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Description: Leveraging large volumes of these recursive track geometry measurements to develop and implement automated machine-learning-based processes for analyzing, predicting, and reporting track locations of concern, including those with significant Inspection report that includes the trending of track geometry measures and time to failure (i.e., maintenance and safety limits)."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2079 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_8_1,  # Technology and data alignment
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "This use case will be used to enable new methods and tools that support the maintenance of life cycle of National Airpsace System (NAS) infrastructure. Used to enable non-Georefereced data to be integrated into digital form."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2080 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Description:  The ongoing work leverages AI/ML in big traffic data analytics to identify roadway geolocations where potential safety issue may exist through the integration of connected vehicle data, speed and Individual Vehicle Record data, historical cr Maps and Reports"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2081 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_3_3,  # Innovation pace and responsiveness
        aiu:BG_8_1,  # Technology and data alignment
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Description: A data science lab established at Turner-Fairbank Highway Research Center. Promote usage of AI/ML tools on Databricks platform and implement research use cases across multiple highway desciplines."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2082 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_3_3,  # Innovation pace and responsiveness
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Description: The Exploratory Advanced Research (EAR) Program addresses the need for longer term, higher risk research with the potential for transformative improvements to transportation systems. The EAR Program currently funds several projects that focus Inputs and outputs vary across the projects."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2083 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_3_3,  # Innovation pace and responsiveness
        aiu:BG_8_1,  # Technology and data alignment
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "DOT-Private Sector collaboration to develop advanced AI data structure expertise, lessons learned, and best practices to accelerate AI development across the agency. High-quality and efficient data structures increase AI model efficiency and accuracy."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2084 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_3,  # Internal controls, procedures, and performance management
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "TrUCKR is the CAIO managed DOT platform for tracking the Department's unclassified AI use case development, maturity, assessments, clearances, risk evaluations and mitigations, and authorities to operate across the use case lifecycle for operations, resea TrUCKR is the Department's data source for prioritizing and driving the acceleration of AI, monitoring AI governance and compliance, and internal and external collaboration."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2085 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_7_1,  # Regulatory and legal compliance
        aiu:BG_7_2,  # Governance structures and board effectiveness
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "The AICA Working Group consists of Operating Administration (OA) and Secretarial Offices AI leaders and subject matter experts across the Department.  It is chaired by the CAIO and vice-chaired by representatives from the DOT Office of Research and Techno Provides DOT with the necessary administrative infrastructure for coordinating Executive Order and other federal guidance and mandates, tracking AI activities, and collaborating on AI initiatives and compliance, governance, and guidance documents."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2086 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_6_1,  # Talent, skills, and workforce strategy
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "The Workforce Acquisitions and Training Team members are DOT OA and Secretarial Office leaders responsible for AI talent acquisition and training and inspiring the workforce to accelerate AI adoption. Provides DOT with coordination and collaboration on AI hiring and training initiatives."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2087 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_7_1,  # Regulatory and legal compliance
        aiu:BG_7_2,  # Governance structures and board effectiveness
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "The SR2 Committee reviews and approves the operational deployment of all AI use cases and the public sharing of use case data, models, and code. The SR2 Committee is also responsible for performing the Security Review required by Executive Order 14110 Sec Provides the Department with expert oversight of AI use case safety, security, rights, privacy, and data."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2088 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_3,  # Internal controls, procedures, and performance management
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "The Procurement Team members are DOT OA and Secretarial Office leaders responsible for AI procurement and acquisitions. Provides DOT with internal and external coordination and collaboration on AI procurement and acquisition policy and procedures."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2089 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_3_3,  # Innovation pace and responsiveness
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "The AI Emerging Technology Team members are DOT OA and Secretarial Office leaders most knowledgeable in leading-edge AI technology, capacity, and capabilities. Provides DOT with internal and external coordination and collaboration on establishing and maintaining leading-edge AI technology, capacity, and capabilities."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2090 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_7_1,  # Regulatory and legal compliance
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Guidelines on usage of commercially available Generative Artificial Intelligence (GenAI) Tools and Services. NHTSA guidelines (do's and don'ts) for using publicly available GenAI services while protecting security and privacy of DOT data."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2091 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_7_1,  # Regulatory and legal compliance
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Provide DOT-wide generative AI (GenAI) policy. Establish guidelines and safeguards for GenAI use within the Department."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2092 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Creating weighting scheme values based on safety data for measuring and monitoring safety risk in the National Air Space. The weights are used to generate safety indices for surface and airborne settings, for both commercial and non-commercial flights. Safety indices for Commercial and Non-Commercial accident and incident categories with the SSM Safety Performance Target."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2093 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Speeds up the development of code structure. Provides programming language recommendations (C#) to support coding/software development."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2094 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "The AI system designed for Tech-Ops personnel is a comprehensive support tool that enhances efficiency by providing rapid, contextually accurate answers drawn from a central Knowledge Library. This Knowledge Library contains Technical Instruction Manuals, Direct Answers to Queries: When a technician inputs a question in plain language, the AI generates a concise, relevant answer drawn directly from the Technical Instruction Manuals, Maintenance Handbooks, or other materials in the Knowledge Library. This r"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2095 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_4_3,  # Internal controls, procedures, and performance management
        aiu:BG_6_1,  # Talent, skills, and workforce strategy
        aiu:BG_7_1,  # Regulatory and legal compliance
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "To allow employees to quickly and easily (via natural language processing) ask Human Resource policy questions and quickly receive back an easy to understand response. The system outputs HR policy in response to questions which are input by users (employees)."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2096 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Improving efficiency and productivity in budget and finance. financial data retrieved from the text resources"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2097 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "CARES will use AI (Azure chatbot) to scan thousands of pages and generate an accurate answer. The benefits will be a faster and deeper understanding of the business requirements so the FAA can speed up our development. The Azure chatbot will find the information requested and output the information in a clear, easy to understand answer."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2098 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_3,  # Internal controls, procedures, and performance management
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "The Financial Policy Chatbot (AI system) will search a variety of financial policy documents to answer users' financial policy questions, and more importantly, will link to the document(s) where it found the answer.  The the chatbot will initially be used The Financial Policy Chatbot (AI system) will search a variety of financial policy documents to answer users' financial policy questions, and more importantly, will link to the document(s) where it found the answer."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2099 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_2_4,  # Customer experience, satisfaction, and retention
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """Intended purpose: To make the user experience of end users more easy and  interactive and engaging.

Benefits: Increased customer satisfaction of FAA's coordination systems' users Responses to help questions"""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2100 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_7_1,  # Regulatory and legal compliance
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "The intended purpose is to provide answers to Element Design Data collection Tool (ED DCT) questions used during COS (continued operational safety), IC (initial certification), and configuration changes of a certificate holder's operation. The benefits in The outputs are aswers to Element Design Data collection Tool (EDDCT) questions."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2101 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "The intended purpose of the AI chatbot is to streamline the retrieval of information from multiple FAA Orders and change notices. The expected benefits include saving time, improving accuracy in finding specific citations, and reducing manual effort for u The chatbot outputs specific citations and relevant sections from multiple FAA Orders and change notices, which provides quick access to  information based on user queries. It delivers clear and concise responses by searching through documents like JO 711"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2102 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """The intended purpose of the AI is to serve as a "Copilot" for technical operations, allowing users to interact with complex data in plain language. This Copilot will retrieve, interpret, and present relevant information from the Instrument Landing Systems "Enhanced Accessibility: Users can pose questions in plain language, bypassing the need for technical know-how on data filtering or analysis, making data insights available to a broader range of personnel.
Time Efficiency: By quickly retrieving relevant d"""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2103 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "To measure and monitor the degree of anomaly or deviation from a baseline based on safety data in the National Air Space to the Service Area, district, and facility level. Day look ahead forecast of anomalous/non-anomalous conditions at levels from NAS-wide down to facilities."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2104 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Using genAI, automatically tag text narratives from Comprehensive Electronic Data Analysis and Reporting (CEDAR) Mandatory Occurrence Reports (MOR's) with factors from Human Performance Common Taxonomy (HP CT) at scale and with significant speed up. HP CT factors related to an MOR's narrative."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2105 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_3_3,  # Innovation pace and responsiveness
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "This use case will be used increase trust in new technology approach through this socialzation exercise. And increase buy-in and education of stakeholders with a useful product from their input. Execute a use case chosen from a collection of candidates from Safety Trend Analytics Dashboard (STAD) stakeholders."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2106 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "This use case will be used to develop and understanding of HP Fatigue recommendations and ties to safety risk. To be determined"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2107 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "To increase expainability and interpretability of changes in safety risk based on contributing factors from and LLM tuned to Human Factors Common Taxonomy. What are the Human Factors Common Taxonomy factors that are associated with a change in safety risk in the NAS."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2108 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_3_2,  # Quality, reliability, and consistency
        aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText """The overall purpose of the effort is to establish Knowledge Graph usage to develop Deep Learning, starting with a specific problem statement. The problem statement is to "Enhance the management and resolution of deviation events by providing actionable in 1. Diagnostic Insights
-	Event Analysis: Contributing factors to a deviation, with root cause identification based on historical and real-time data.
-	Priority Assessment: Highlight of critical issues requiring immediate attention, ranked by severity and"""^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_DOT_2109 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_1,  # Product safety, data protection, and incident prevention
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "AIR is utilizing AI within Palantir Foundry (i.e., Foundry's \"Artificial Intelligence Platform\" (AIP)) to search, find and link similar types of events (e.g., Continued Operational Safety (COS) event reports, Notices of Noncompliance (NCN), semantic searc The output aggregates information from disparate sources to provide an integrated view of events that are similar."^^xsd:string .

