        aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "The Clearinghouse Network is a series of online communities hosted on the Roundtable platform. These communities, including any AI features, are not open to the general public. Members of these communities are state or local election officials. The AI tools in this platform are intended to meet the needs of election officials by providing summaries for longer text or video based content. Summarized text and video transcripts."^^xsd:string .

