    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Enhances security and compliance in file sharing and collaboration by detecting anomalies and potential threats in real-time.\" Kiteworks employs AI to enhance security and compliance in file sharing and collaboration by detecting anomalies and potential threats."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_FHFA_1369 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
