        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Commonlook Online is used to translate complex mathematical formula into plain language for publicly released documents. Commonlook Online is used to translate complex mathematical formula into plain language for publicly released documents."^^xsd:string .

