    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "The Apple iOS platform provides multiple applications with Natural Language Processing (NLP) capability.  This is a predictive word  technology where the platfom makes an assumption in real time of the word that user is going to type, and allows for a single tap selection. The Apple iOS platform provides multiple applications with Natural Language Processing (NLP) capability.  This is a predictive word technology where the platform makes an assumption in real time of the word that user is going to type and allows for a single tap selection."^^xsd:string .

