aiu:plan_2024_NSF_905 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_2_4,  # Customer experience, satisfaction, and retention
        aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "ServiceNow GenAI is a FedRAMP High certified system to accelerate digital transformation using Now Assist. Automatically generate content such as responses, work notes, and knowledgebase articles related to customer service experience. Increase productivity and speed to delivery with intelligent recommendations. Resolve issues swiftly with chatbots that understand human language. Increase productivity and speed to delivery with intelligent recommendations. Resolve issues swiftly with chatbots that understand human language."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_NSF_906 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_4_3,  # Internal controls, procedures, and performance management
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "The Budget Area Topic Classification Tool uses a pre-trained BERT model ('bert-base-uncased') to classify proposals into 1 of 8 budget areas: Advanced Manufacturing, AI, Advanced Wireless, Clean Energy, Microelectronics & Semiconductors, Quantum, or Trustworthy AI. This approach is semi-supervised in nature as the training data is comprised of pre-tagged CISE proposals from prior years. Upon training the model to learn the multi-label structure of the underlying data, the model's accuracy and discriminatory power was tested using a hold-out sample (i.e. 80/20 split). The model outputs a numerical vector of probabilities representing the likelihood that a given proposal belongs to 1 or more categories. A cut-off value can then be set for determining final classification for a given proposal."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_NSF_907 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Commercial-off-the-shelf (COTS) - The AI system was purchased pre-built from a third-party, Wellsaid has been used to generate placeholder voice over, which will be replaced later by real voice over, so it doesnt cause much AI policy concerns. allowing the agency to skip design and development by federal or contract personnel."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_NSF_908 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "OLPA's Creative Services team will use Photoshop's AI-powered tools to refine edits of photos and graphics, particularly the retouching of portraits."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_NSF_909 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_3,  # Internal controls, procedures, and performance management
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "The resubmit checker takes a list of proposal IDs and returns a list of similar proposals submitted to NSF in the past, scored by their similarity. This is useful for identifying resubmitted proposals for several purposes: evaluating whether to return without review for lack of revision, ensuring continuity of merit review, and the analysis of broader resubmit trends."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_NSF_910 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_3_3,  # Innovation pace and responsiveness
        aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Within software development, AI-driven tools, such as AWS CodeWhisperer, Amazon Q and Bedrock, and integration with development workflow, promise to elevate developer productivity and refine code quality. . The objective of this pilot is to explore potential integration of these AWS services with DIS Developers IDEs, Jenkins automation, Bitbucket, laying the groundwork for Secure AI Assisted Development at NSF"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_NSF_911 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_6_1,  # Talent, skills, and workforce strategy
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Airtable is a low code platform that incorporates Open AI.  The Open AI services are purchased by and the data is kept private to Airtable.  TIP has been approved to use Airtable for several usecases and Airtable has been certified as secure by the NSF OCIO Security Team. to use Airtable to trial Airtable's AI's ability to match potential reviewer expertise to the reviewer."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_NSF_912 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_6_1,  # Talent, skills, and workforce strategy
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "TIP is authorized to use Airtable for project management including reviewer volunteers and recruitment.  Airtable is a no-code platform that includes a built-in database.  We do not store any PII in our database except for &quot;public PII&quot; such as name, position, work email address, areas of professional expertise, etc. 1. Airtable AI is prompted to look at the potential reviewers Linked In profile and identify or update the potential reviewers expertise in its database based on recent updates to professional experience in LinkedIn 2 Search existing potential Submitters database for state associated with submitters institution"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_NSF_913 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_3,  # Internal controls, procedures, and performance management
        aiu:BG_7_1,  # Regulatory and legal compliance
        aiu:BG_8_1,  # Technology and data alignment
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Per the CHIPS and Science Act mandate, TIP needs to know our investment portfolio based on the 10 KTA. Enhancing TIP Awards: Efficient Tagging for the 10 Key Technology Areas (KTA)"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_NSF_914 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_2_4,  # Customer experience, satisfaction, and retention
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "The key objective of this effort is to create and test machine-learning-backed or artificial intelligence (AI)-backed user experiences with federal statistical data. This experience shall improve on the current state of user interactions based on obtaining answers to questions via search engines or emailing federal staff or contractors. This project seeks to develop and pilot an AI chat bot (or the like) that answers users text queries submitted via an interface. Answers will be obtained from public statistical data of federal statistical agencies in this project."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_NSF_915 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "No tool has been selected yet, exploring tools tht may help with sorting requests"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_NSF_916 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_10_4,  # Alignment with stakeholder expectations and social impact
        aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_7_1,  # Regulatory and legal compliance
        aiu:BG_8_1,  # Technology and data alignment
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Exploring using a ChatGPT integration with NSFs Digital Asset Management system (DAM), for the images we host there. to generate alt text for images we'll be using in digital communication products (such as nsf.gov) to ensure theyre accessible to individuals using assistive technology."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_NSF_917 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_3_4,  # Product portfolio and lifecycle management
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Exploring whether the application of BERTopic modeling (or a similar NLP method) is applicable to a portfolio analysis. xploring whether it is applicable to portfolio analysis"^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_NSF_918 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_2_2,  # Market understanding, demand estimation, and segmentation
        aiu:BG_8_1,  # Technology and data alignment
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Exploring the use of unsupervised NLP to identify topical themes within responses submitted to the NSF public engagement questionnaire. The AI system will include multiple open-source techniques used together to achieve this goal. To develop a cluster model to be applied to all responses. Where feasible, the RTI STEM education experts/analysts will manually map the research topics to NSF research programs."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_NSF_919 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_4_1,  # Process efficiency and waste reduction
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "We propose using a Commercial Off the Shelf AWS product, Textract, as a character recognition tool Handwritten text will be an open format question for science and engineering and some optional check boxes for demographic and other data questions. to convert handwritten text into machine-encoded text for a postcard."^^xsd:string .

aiu:plan_2024_NSF_920 a aiu:AIUseCasePlan ;
    aiu:hasBusinessGoal aiu:BG_3_3,  # Innovation pace and responsiveness
        aiu:BG_8_3 ;  # Automation and AI enablement
    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "Ask NSF initial pilot is intended to test the hypothesis that a chatbot can be rapidly created using an AI Platform. Answer general questions from existing documents"^^xsd:string .

