    aiu:purposeBenefitsText "FDA-cleared medical device to assist clinicians and improve healthcare outcomes. Described in FDA documentation for this device (https://www.accessdata.fda.gov/cdrh_docs/pdf19/K193248.pdf)."^^xsd:string .

