    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "The AI will transcript audio/video data and provide a printable artifact. The AI only provides recommendations the final usable data is reviewed and certified by TSA staff."^^xsd:string .

