    aiu:outputsText "The system produces an recommendation to the Transportation Security Officer (TSO) to indicate if person presenting the identity document is similar to the face on the photo ID document.  In the event of a non-match, the TSO is responsible for additional identity verification steps to verify the identity of the traveler."^^xsd:string ;
