    aiu:outputsText "TSA is leveraging CBP's TVS system technology as an optional process for passengers or crew members traveling via certain airports who wish to further expedite their TSA PreCheck or crew member ID verification process. This additional TSA PreCheck feature is voluntary, and passengers may opt-out of the process at any time and instead choose the standard identity verification by a Transportation Security Officer (TSO). Crew members that wish to opt-out will be sent to the security checkpoint to process through screening."^^xsd:string ;
    aiu:saopReviewed true ;
    aiu:usesPII true .

