    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "Text Analytics does not make predictions, recommendations, or decisions. It is merely a research tool that identifies potential patterns, while remaining agnostic as to whether those patterns identify potential fraud, national security, and/or public safety concerns. Instead, trained staff evaluate the patterns to determine whether they identify potential concerns and then validate and/or invalidate those potential concerns through the course of their investigations or adjudications."^^xsd:string ;
    aiu:saopReviewed true ;
    aiu:usesPII true .

