    aiu:outputsText "Eliminates need for manual review by extracting unique names and DOBs from IdHS documents and when names/DOBs already in ELIS, ANH will not suggest any names.This is still a human in the loop process. The ELIS user performing MNH tasks prompted to make a decision if the suggested names and DOBs are related to case hence are able to accept/reject the suggestions."^^xsd:string ;
