    aiu:outputsText "Responses back to a user dashboard accessible internally only by VAC Management and Program Analyst (MPA) personnel.  Keywords relating to the MPA's work interest are extracted if present and risk scores are assigned to the open-source collected information. The data is presented to the MPA on the GUI (graphical user interface) dashboard."^^xsd:string ;
    aiu:saopReviewed false ;
    aiu:usesPII false .

