    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "The system  aggregates vast amounts of publicly and commercially available data from diverse sources, such as social media, news streams, company records, and even the dark web, to provide insights on potential threats and risks, that can be used as actionable intelligence reports, risk assessments, and alerts that support CBP personnel  in real-time decision-making and long-term strategic planning."^^xsd:string ;
    aiu:saopReviewed true ;
    aiu:usesPII true .

aiu:proc_2024_DHS_20 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_Initiated ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_DHS_20_init ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "The AI system is intended to output custom reports on identified vulnerabilities within application programing interfaces (APIs). These reports will include the identified risk and a summary of the risk, as well as tailored remediation guidance based on the applications, environment, data, and tests conducted for end-users."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_DHS_21 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_Initiated ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_DHS_21_init ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "The technology enables the accurate detection of malicious activity in the cyber environment for actionable insights so that leadership can identify threats and efficiently mitigate them while reducing the cost of other security defenses. With the technology, the user will be alerted of detected compromise, evaluation of the creation of decoys, and the monitoring/analysis of interaction with the decoys from the adversary."^^xsd:string .

