    aiu:outputsText "The Machine Learning Translation Technology Initiative will offer real-time communication/translation services to assist personnel in providing meaningful access to programs and services for limited English proficient (LEP) noncitizens. AI will be used to provide voice to text, text to voice, and voice to voice translations in at least 21 languages."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_DHS_97 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
