    aiu:outputsText "The outputs provides answers to frequently asked policy and guidance questions and summaries and drafts for more in-depth analysis of policy issues. All responses go to an SEVP staff member and are not the final work product."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_DHS_98 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
