    aiu:outputsText "SID answers frequently asked questions from callers. If the SID cannot answer a callers question, it turns the caller over to an agent in the response center. The chatbot captures the interaction with the caller and sends the information via an API to Student and Exchange Visitor Program Automated Management System (SEVPAMS)."^^xsd:string .

