    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "IOCR will speed the flow of data to the certifying officer for review and ultimate payment.  This capability also has broader potential to enhance data extraction, validation, and preservation.  IOCR will be deployed in conjunction with Robotics Process Automation to allow for more comprehensive automation solutions. The same robust testing and validation of automations prior to deployment to production will be applied to IOCR"^^xsd:string .

