aiu:proc_2024_DOJ_1757 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_OpsMaint ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "The AI features within Adobe Suite products generate automated enhancements and suggestions to improve the efficiency and quality of multimedia content handling. In applications like Photoshop and Acrobat, the AI provides functionalities such as image enhancement, optical character recognition (OCR), content-aware editing, and automated formatting. For example, the AI tool might automatically adjust image lighting and colors, recognize and convert scanned text into editable formats, or suggest layout improvements for documents. These outputs assist users by automating routine tasks and enhancing the quality of the final product. These AI tools support staff in their work, but all actions are initiated and finalized by human users, ensuring that control remains with the individual operator."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_DOJ_1758 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_OpsMaint ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Both ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "The AI features generate alerts, highlight uncommon travel paths/profiles, suggesting beneficial attention areas."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_DOJ_1759 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_OpsMaint ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Both ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "Bounding boxes for video frames and metadata regarding the detected object characteristics, alphanumeric digitized text from OCR"^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_DOJ_1760 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_OpsMaint ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "The Alation Data Catalog AI system primarily produces outputs that are recommendations and predictive insights to enhance data discovery, governance, and usability. These outputs include data recommendations, where the AI suggests relevant datasets or reports based on user behavior and usage patterns, as well as search predictions, which anticipate what users are looking for and suggests relevant terms as they type. The system also generates informational insights, such as data lineage and usage trends, to help users understand data quality and provenance. Additionally, Alations AI feature provides governance alerts, flagging assets that may need review to ensure compliance and accuracy. Rather than making decisions, the AI outputs guide users toward more efficient and informed data management."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_DOJ_1761 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_OpsMaint ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Both ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "Notifications to law enforcement based upon preconfigured alerts from AI-enabled analysis of data streams from participating security devices"^^xsd:string .

