aiu:proc_2024_DOJ_1779 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_AcqDev ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Rights ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "The AI system produces two key outputs. First, it identifies and isolates certain data fields. Then, it converts the data from these specific data fields into digitized text using OCR. This text is used to create a limited searchable index , which points firearm trace processors to potential responsive records. This streamlined process makes firearm tracing faster and more efficient, replacing the need for manual searches through scanned forms."^^xsd:string .

