    aiu:outputsText "The output of the autocoder is a classification prediction. In the context of event type, it takes raw text like 'shoplifting' runs the raw code through an LLM and predicts which of our established categories that event belongs in, in this case \"Property Crime: Theft\". The output of the packaged tool is a dataset with these classifications appended to the raw CAD file."^^xsd:string .

