    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "The output of this autocoder is common definitions for offense charge classification. It has been trained on an offense crosswalk for the BJS National Corrections Reporting Program (NCRP) (https://www.icpsr.umich.edu/files/NACJD/ncrp/Offense_Code_Crosswalk.xlsx) to convert plain-text offense descriptions into classifications routinely used by the NCRP."^^xsd:string .

