    aiu:outputsText "emPOWER AI gives the user publicly available data from the HHS emPOWER Map on the number of electricity-dependent Medicare beneficiaries at the national, state, territory, county, and ZIP Code levels. It also provides information on other HHS emPOWER Program tools and resources that collectively support emergency preparedness, response, recovery, mitigation, and resilience activities."^^xsd:string ;
