    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "This solution automatically determines the relevancy of published journal articles. Relevant articles are included in a master dataset that is linked to a PowerBI"^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_644 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_644_acq ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_WidelyAvailable ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_InHouse ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_AcqDev ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_644_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_Limited ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "The AI analyzes the textual content of APRs. We have started our analysis by focusing on the sections detailing the challenges faced by ICRCs during the 2019 funding cycle. The AI identifies key themes, trends, and critical information that may require further attention. The AI methodology extracts insights and patterns from the data, which can then be compared with manual qualitative analysis outcomes. In subsequent stages, the AI will be expanded to analyze other sections of the APRs, such as progress toward goals and program impact."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_645 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_645_acq ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_Partial ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_InHouse ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_AcqDev ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_645_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_Limited ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "Two machine learning models will be created, one for internal use and another for public release. In both instances, these models will be utilized alongside rule-based text analysis to ascertain whether a patient in a hospital setting has used a drug therapeutically (in accordance with medical prescription) or non-therapeutically. This information is used to gather new insights from EHRs for health statistics published through the NHCS."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_646 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_646_acq ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_Complete ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_InHouse ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_AcqDev ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_646_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_NoDocs ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "This AI assistant will use retrieval augmented generation (RAG) to return information related to HIV based on a user's query and other documents."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_647 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_647_acq ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_Complete ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_InHouse ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_AcqDev ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_647_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_Limited ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "The fuzzy matching tool uses pre-trained, open source LLMs to identify similar records between eClearance submissions and CDC-authored publications. This tool is intended for internal use only."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_648 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_648_acq ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_Partial ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_InHouse ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_AcqDev ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_648_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_Limited ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "The Through APIs, large language models are used to review a large number of abstracts to help identify which kinds of groups may be least likely to obtain vaccines in the global space--marginalized groups within country, for example."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_649 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_649_acq ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_Complete ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_InHouse ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_AcqDev ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_649_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_NoDocs ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "This AI assistant will use retrieval augmented generation (RAG) to return information related to HIV based on a user's query. Our aim is to input all dataset documentation and metadata into an index with the goal of creating a virtual assistant. This assistant offers support to our HIV researchers by providing the information they seek from the data and potentially generating SAS, R, or Python code for desired variable names. For instance, if we require a dataset containing HIV PrEP information, we can request it to generate a list of current datasets that contain data on PrEP medication usage in 2019, along with the associated variable names. Subsequently, we can instruct it to produce lines of code, such as a logistic regression, which can be readily copied and pasted into our analysis software of choice. Another example would be if our researchers would like information returned about a given dataset, this assistant could return specific information based on the researcher's query."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_650 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_650_acq ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_Complete ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_Both ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_AcqDev ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_650_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_NoDocs ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "The Division of Nutrition, Physical Activity, and Obesity within CDC's National Center for Chronic Disease Prevention and Health Promotion aims to explore and advance the use of machine learning methods for identifying sidewalks, bicycle lanes, and other relevant infrastructure in various types of images, including satellite and roadway images. The input data would consist of image-based data, while the outputs could take the form of geocoded data tables, maps, GIS layers, or summary reports. The goal is to develop and promote these techniques to enhance understanding and analysis of built environments related to physical activity."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_651 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_651_acq ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_WidelyAvailable ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_Both ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_AcqDev ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_651_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_Developed ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText """This AI solution (chatbot) uses Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG) to retrieve and synthesize information from a limited set of publicly available IIS guidance documents related to the HL7 Electronic Exchange Standard specification, Clinical Decision Support for Immunization (CDSi) and IIS Operational Best Practices. It does this using a Question-and-Answer style interface, allowing team members to retrieve answers in an efficient and user-friendly way.
On 07/26/2024 the CDC Information Technology and Data Governance (ITDG) Executive Committee has approved this investment to use AI to create a system that can conduct a dialogue with a user and answer questions about the contents of already approved public documents."""^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_652 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_652_acq ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_Missing ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_Contracting ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_AcqDev ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_652_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_Developed ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "This AI uses natural language process to (1) identify potentially relevant articles and prioritize them for screening, (2) retrieve PDFs from PubMed, and (3) suggest data in PDFs for extraction."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_653 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_653_acq ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_Partial ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_Both ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_AcqDev ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_653_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_NoDocs ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "NewsScape is a AI enabled news aggregation and summarization that is hosted within the 1CDP platform. The main motivation to build  NewsScape was to develop a system that uses Large Language Models (LLMs) to surface relevant insight from recent news articles. NewsScape ingests a high volume of news articles, in the order of thousands of news articles everyday, and surfaces the information from them that related to the topic we were interested (for example, pathogen related news articles, or U.S. medical supply chain updates).  The tool can be customized based on specific program office needs, and can be deployed independently of one another so that one program office can have their own custom version of NewsScape installed."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_654 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_654_acq ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_Missing ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_Contracting ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_AcqDev ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_654_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_Limited ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "An internal web application  will enable CDC users to: 1) import and securely store policy or program documents; 2) search for relevant documents; 3) ask questions of relevant text segments; 4) validate answers; and 5) collaborate on policy surveillance and evaluation projects."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_655 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_655_acq ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_WidelyAvailable ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_InHouse ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_AcqDev ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_655_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_Limited ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "The intent of this project is to identify failed wastewater systems, which can be sources of soil and drinking water contamination as well as vectors that carry or transmit disease in the community."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_656 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_656_acq ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_Complete ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_Contracting ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_AcqDev ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_656_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_NoDocs ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "CDC's National Center for Chronic Disease Prevention and Health Promotion use of Generative AI in this use case is to help convert existing web content into plain and clear language. This solution uses Gen AI to create new versions of publicly available content that are easier for end-users to understand. By incorporating prompts, the tool makes the content more suitable for a general lay audience. In addition to web articles, the Generative AI tool also allows for the creation of social media posts. The goal of this project is to make information more accessible by providing plain language content on various platforms. CDC sometimes uses GenAI (generative artificial intelligence) to help create content for the public. This may include content for the web, social media, fact sheets, and graphics. In every case, our experts review our communication materials in an effort to ensure accuracy and quality before use. CDC public health research, data, and recommendations are based on the best science currently available and go through a separate agency review process prior to release."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_657 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_657_acq ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_Partial ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_InHouse ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_AcqDev ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_657_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_Limited ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "This AI generates transcripts from recorded interviews for staff to use when performing qualitative research to assist with Federal Health Survey research."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_658 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_658_acq ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_Partial ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_InHouse ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_AcqDev ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_658_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_Limited ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "Generates clusters of similar public comments to a 'notice of proposed rulemaking' to aid in manual review."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_659 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:customCodePresent true ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_659_acq ;
    aiu:hasCodeAccess aiu:CA_PublicSource ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_Complete ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_Both ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_ImplAssess ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_659_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_Published ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "This project  models disease spread and impact based upon a set of models, a variety of data sources, and allows for the inclusion of the impact of potential public health actions such as vaccinations. These insights can be used by public health decision makers to inform current and future responses to public health emergencies"^^xsd:string ;
    aiu:saopReviewed false ;
    aiu:usesPII false .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_660 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:customCodePresent true ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_660_acq ;
    aiu:hasCodeAccess aiu:CA_PrivateSource ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_Missing ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_Both ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_ImplAssess ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_660_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_Developed ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "When the user enters a prompt or query related to data extraction into the chatbot, the tool uses a GPT-4 model and Azure AI Search within a RAG architecture to retrieve relevant sections of text from the provided enterprise data sources and extract key information as instructed by the users prompt."^^xsd:string ;
    aiu:saopReviewed false ;
    aiu:usesPII false .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_661 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:customCodePresent true ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_661_acq ;
    aiu:hasCodeAccess aiu:CA_PrivateSource ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_Missing ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_Both ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_ImplAssess ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_661_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_Developed ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "When the user enters a prompt or query related to summarization into the chatbot, the tool uses a GPT-4 model and Azure AI Search within a RAG architecture to retrieve relevant sections of text from the provided enterprise data sources and condense that information into concise summaries in response to the users prompt."^^xsd:string ;
    aiu:saopReviewed false ;
    aiu:usesPII false .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_662 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:customCodePresent true ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_662_acq ;
    aiu:hasCodeAccess aiu:CA_PrivateSource ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_Partial ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_InHouse ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_ImplAssess ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_662_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_Limited ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "AI is used in this case to generate suggested metadata fields based upon existing metadata information provided by a dataset. These tags would then be used for staff accessing the enterprise data catalogue to discover datasets and find connections to support existing on-going work."^^xsd:string ;
    aiu:saopReviewed false ;
    aiu:usesPII false .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_663 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:customCodePresent true ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_663_acq ;
    aiu:hasCodeAccess aiu:CA_PrivateSource ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_WidelyAvailable ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_InHouse ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_ImplAssess ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_663_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_Published ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "Algorithm examines a sequence barcode/genotype (our use case is for malaria, but it can be applied to other contexts) and it assigns the malaria parasite genotype to a geographic origin, which may be a continent or some other geographic regional category. While this use case has the barcode as a set of genetic loci from malaria parasites, and the categories are geographic (i.e., continents, subregions), the algorithm could be trained to assign genetic barcodes from other pathogens to any number of different categories assuming the appropriate training dataset exists."^^xsd:string ;
    aiu:saopReviewed false ;
    aiu:usesPII false .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_664 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:customCodePresent true ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_664_acq ;
    aiu:hasCodeAccess aiu:CA_PrivateSource ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_Partial ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_InHouse ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_ImplAssess ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_664_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_Published ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_EmergencyMgmt ;
    aiu:outputsText "This system uses publicly available Facebook posts from approximately 40,000 school or district Facebook accounts. Then uses a large language model to categorize posts as unplanned school closure for several types of events (weather, health, facility issues, safety). It also will denote the type of status change (full closure, virtual, hybrid, or early / late dismissal). The data is checked and recoded (if needed) by a staff person every 24 hours."^^xsd:string ;
    aiu:saopReviewed false ;
    aiu:usesPII false .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_665 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:customCodePresent true ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_665_acq ;
    aiu:hasCodeAccess aiu:CA_PrivateSource ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_Missing ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_InHouse ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_ImplAssess ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_665_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_Limited ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "Reviewing the public comments currently involves a manual review process that necessitates a high level of time and effort on the part of regulatory analysts. To improve the process of reviewing public comments as part of regulatory analysis, our team implemented topic modeling (Grootendorst et al., 2022) and sentiment analysis (Hartman et al., 2023) of comments published to the new amendment to foreign quarantine regulation published by CDC on July 10, 2023. This solution expands these efforts by using generative AI models  to try for capture stance expressed in each comment. While there is also an option to manually label and train models for stance detection, custom-trained text classification models may not be transferable to future rules due to rule-specific discussions and arguments. In contrast, using generative AI models for stance detection can be transferable to future rules irrespective of the discussion contexts and arguments."^^xsd:string ;
    aiu:saopReviewed false ;
    aiu:usesPII false .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_666 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_Initiated ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_666_init ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "The objective of this project is to take unstructured data, clean it, and use pretrained Named Entity Recognition (NER) tools to extract signs/symptoms in deidentified electronic health records that can be used to characterize a cohort or make further analysis."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_667 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_Initiated ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_667_init ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "The model will take a de-identified free-text description of the patient's emergency department visit encounter, along with a handful of other pre-coded variables, and output the probability that the encounter meets the case definition."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_668 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_Initiated ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_668_init ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "We propose to use a Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) framework for two primary functions: It converts natural language lab protocols into precise XML workflows that are compatible with Clarity LIMS. This conversion process involves understanding technical documentations and generating corresponding script code. In addition, it serves as an interactive knowledge base for documentation of Clarity LIMS and Laboratory Quality Management and Regulations."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_669 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_Initiated ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_669_init ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "CDC's Division of Global Migration Health receives inquires for information which is available publicly in some form but may be hard to find and requires staff responding to these inquiries to have a broad knowledge and can be time intensive to respond to. The AI Chatbot will draft an initial response to questions using content available on CDCs public-facing webpages. Each response goes through the existing CDC clearance process regardless of if AI is used, but the Chatbot helps provide an initial draft based on previously published content. The goal is to help with responding to different inquiries the division receives, including but not limited to CDC-INFO and media."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_670 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_Initiated ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_670_init ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "Machine learning will be used to more efficiently screen research articles relevant to evaluating the effectiveness of an intervention."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_671 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_Initiated ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_671_init ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "This AI assistant will use retrieval augmented generation (RAG) to return information related to HIV based on a user's query. Our aim is to input all dataset documentation and metadata into an index with the goal of creating a virtual assistant. This assistant offers support to our HIV researchers by providing the information they seek from the data and potentially generating SAS, R, or Python code for desired variable names. For instance, if we require a dataset containing HIV PrEP information, we can request it to generate a list of current datasets that contain data on PrEP medication usage in 2019, along with the associated variable names. Subsequently, we can instruct it to produce lines of code, such as a logistic regression, which can be readily copied and pasted into our analysis software of choice. Another example would be if our researchers would like information returned about a given dataset, this assistant could return specific information based on the researcher's query."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_672 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_Initiated ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_672_init ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "The goal of this solution is to evaluate how AI can be implemented in the process of summarizing subject matter expert (SME) interpretations/knowledge to improve efficiency in knowledge dissemination during a response.  As part of the proof-of-concept, we  seek to evaluate the limitations and uncertainties of AI methods in this use-case, such as bias and hallucinations as such issues will require mitigation before this method can be broadly adopted. Our proposed approach would make use of the ChatGPT interface through EDAV (or alternative accepted platform) as our prompts will include uncleared data from the Respiratory Virus Response (RVR). In this response,  SMEs from different groups provide bulleted information that then needs to be further summarized to address key takeaways.   Bullets from prior weeks will prompt AI to generate summaries. The initial approach will focus on engineering prompts to get key takeaways while future iterations may require fine-tuning to allow for better contextualization of responses as well as improvements in tone and style."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_673 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_Initiated ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_673_init ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "The AI used a LLM to extract data from an abstract review and categorize relevant themes and topics into a user-friendly dashboard. This dashboard can be used by a health scientist to pull resources from 2012-2022   for specific school closure outcomes or themes."^^xsd:string .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_674 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:customCodePresent true ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_674_acq ;
    aiu:hasCodeAccess aiu:CA_PrivateSource ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_WidelyAvailable ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_Both ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_OpsMaint ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasImplementationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_674_impl ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_674_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_Published ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "This chatbot, powered by Azure OpenAI Large Language Models, will generate responses to questions asked by the user. In this case, responses will be recommendations on edits for content provided by the user such as a draft email. The chatbot's output can then be copied and pasted or manually entered based upon the users review. CDC sometimes uses GenAI (generative artificial intelligence) to help create content for the public. This may include content for the web, social media, fact sheets, and graphics. In every case, our experts review our communication materials in an effort to ensure accuracy and quality before use. CDC public health research, data, and recommendations are based on the best science currently available and go through a separate agency review process prior to release."^^xsd:string ;
    aiu:saopReviewed false ;
    aiu:usesPII false .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_675 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:customCodePresent true ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_675_acq ;
    aiu:hasCodeAccess aiu:CA_PrivateSource ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_WidelyAvailable ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_Both ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_OpsMaint ;
    aiu:hasImpactType aiu:IT_Neither ;
    aiu:hasImplementationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_675_impl ;
    aiu:hasInitiationTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_675_init ;
    aiu:hasInternalReviewLevel aiu:IR_Published ;
    aiu:hasTopicArea aiu:TA_MissionEnabling ;
    aiu:outputsText "This chatbot, powered by Azure OpenAI Large Language Models, will generate responses to questions asked by the user, in this case about some larger piece of text and any specific pieces of information to extract. The chatbot's output can then be copied and pasted or manually entered into the appropriate testing process by the staff to ensure any code used from the chatbot's output meets the criteria of the current task."^^xsd:string ;
    aiu:saopReviewed false ;
    aiu:usesPII false .

aiu:proc_2024_HHS_676 a aiu:AIUseCaseProcess ;
    aiu:customCodePresent true ;
    aiu:hasAcqDevTime aiu:ti_proc_2024_HHS_676_acq ;
    aiu:hasCodeAccess aiu:CA_PrivateSource ;
    aiu:hasDataDocLevel aiu:DDL_WidelyAvailable ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentMethod aiu:DM_Both ;
    aiu:hasDevelopmentStage aiu:DS_OpsMaint ;
