    aiu:outputsText "Develop conversational ChatBots (Public Flu, Public COVID-19 Vaccination, Internal Knowledge-Bot) that analyze free text questions entered by the public, healthcare providers, partners, and internal staff, and provide agency-cleared answers which best match the question. Developed in collaboration with Microsoft staff during COVID-19 pandemic using their Cognitive Services, Search, QnA Maker, Azure Healthcare Bot, Power Automate, SharePoint, and webapps."^^xsd:string ;
