    aiu:outputsText "The document summarization tool will allow users to upload documents and produce a summary of these documents. The tool will have enhanced data privacy mechanisms. Additionally, the tool will not use any SAMHSA-provided input as training data, ensuring that private information stays private to SAMHSA."^^xsd:string .

