    aiu:outputsText "The AI system detects the bands present on the LPA strip and outputs the sensitivity to different drugs, automatically classifying the test results as resistant or susceptible. It generates a final diagnostic report that helps clinicians make informed treatment decisions based on the presence or absence of drug resistance"^^xsd:string ;
