    aiu:outputsText "Xtract One View is equipped with advanced analytical tools that process vast amounts of data to detect unusual patterns and potential threats before they escalate. Using machine learning algorithms, it continuously improves its concealed weapons detection capabilities, adapting to new types of risks and optimizing security protocols accordingly."^^xsd:string ;
