    aiu:outputsText "The PAA System automates the process of ingesting PA requests, retrieving requested records, and redacting requested records when necessary. The outputs of the PAA System are reviewed by Deloittes managed service team and by the VA for accuracy and completeness before the requested records are sent to the requester. The outputs consist of records held by VBA within Claim Evidence (VBMS) that have appropriate redactions applied for 3rd party information before release to the 1st party requestor or their designee."^^xsd:string ;
