    aiu:outputsText "The AI program extracts information from a request form (pdf) attached to an email. The information is then populated in an Excel spreadsheet.  The data points include the date of request, date transport needed, name of requesting facility, person completing the form, Veteran's last name, first name and last 4, attendance needed, trip type, pick up time, appointment time, facility pick up address, appt location, destination address, oxygen needed, weight of patient."^^xsd:string ;
